OL,6,FPolice say they have contacted the
OL,7,Ffamilies of 35 people whose bodies
OL,8,Fwere removed from a funeral home after
OL,9,Fconcerns were raised about its care
OL,10,Ffor the dead.
OL,12,FOfficers from Humberside Police have
OL,13,Falso said more than 1,500 calls have
OL,14,Fbeen made to a special phone line set
OL,15,Fup as part of the investigation into
OL,16,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors,
OL,17,Fbased in .
