OL,6,FAn inquiry was launched after a
OL,7,Fcomplaint was made about the "storage
OL,8,Fand management processes relating to
OL,9,Fcare of the deceased" on 6 March.
OL,11,FThirty-five bodies, along with ashes,
OL,12,Fwere subsequently removed from the
OL,13,Fhome on Hessle Road in what police
OL,14,Fdescribed as a "horrific incident".
