OL,6,FIn an update on Friday, Assistant
OL,7,FChief Constable Thom McLoughlin said:
OL,8,F"Working in partnership with His
OL,9,FMajesty's Coroner, I can confirm that,
OL,10,Fwhilst formal identification
OL,11,Fprocedures are ongoing, we do believe
OL,12,Fwe have contacted all families of the
OL,13,F35 deceased.
OL,15,F"My specialist trained officers
OL,16,Fcontinue to support the families
OL,17,Finvolved at this extremely difficult
OL,18,Ftime whilst lengthy enquiries are
OL,19,Fongoing."
