OL,6,FAlong with a team of 120 police and
OL,7,Fcivilian staff, experts from the
OL,8,FNational Crime Agency are involved in
OL,9,Fthe investigation.
OL,11,FA police scene guard remains in place
OL,12,Fat Hessle Road, but searches finished
OL,13,Fon Thursday, Mr McLoughlin said.
OL,15,F"In the last seven days, we have
OL,16,Freceived over 1,500 calls from those
OL,17,Fwho have used Legacy Independent
OL,18,FFuneral Directors," he added.
