OL,6,F"I am aware that this has been a
OL,7,Fworrying time for our communities, and
OL,8,FI want to thank them for their help
OL,9,Fand patience throughout the start of
OL,10,Fthis investigation.
OL,12,F"This has truly been an awful incident
OL,13,Fand the families are understandably
OL,14,Fdistraught and have many questions,
OL,15,Fand we are doing everything we
OL,16,Fpossibly can to give them the answers
OL,17,Fthey deserve."
OL,19,FHe called on people not to
OL,20,F"jeopardise" the investigation and and
OL,21,Fto "refrain from speculating".
